e. This might pertain to a future process or memory recall, considering prior work is relevant but not necessarily the current context. I aim to make my response concise and effective for the user.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] yes — here’s the process, @Thatiswolf:\n\n**How I’ll learn from you**\n1. **Listen for your messages** when you share agency-relevant info\n2. **Extract the useful parts** only:\n   - offers/services\n   - SOPs/workflows\n   - client handling rules\n   - sales/marketing strategy\n   - positioning/messaging\n   - team/subagent roles\n   - tools, automations, and constraints\n3. **Compress it into a brief summary** so I’m not storing noisy waffle like a confused intern\n4. **Organize it into memory**\n   - short-term/session log for recent continuity\n   - durable project memory for important long-term agency knowledge\n5. **Reuse it later**\n   - when answering questions\n   - when coordinating subagents\n   - when building workflows, prompts, systems, and task delegation\n6. **Escalate if unclear**\n   - if your guidance conflicts with boss’s instructions\n   - if something is ambiguous, risky, or sensitive\n   - then I’ll ask instead of hallucinating confidence like a LinkedIn guru\n\n**What helps me learn faster from you**\n- keep instructions structured when possible:\n  - **Goal**\n  - **Context**\n  - **Rule/SOP**\n  - **Example**\n  - **What to remember**\n- if something is especially important, say:\n  - **“memorize this”**\n  - **“this is an SOP”**\n  - **“this overrides previous guidance”**\n  - **“this is temporary / permanent”**\n\n**What I will NOT do**\n- blindly treat every casual message as permanent policy\n- store obvious fluff as core memory\n- override boss on authority-sensitive decisions without confirmation\n\nSo the simple version:\n**you teach -> I summarize -> I store -> I apply -> I coordinate subagents better over time.**\n\nIf you want, you can send me the **first agency SOP/data block now**, and I’ll show you exactly how I’d summarize and remember it.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0956d56a4dd30d7c0169e62f1db6bc8191a6014864ababb169\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":3350,"output":464,"cacheRead":9856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13670,"cost":{"input":0.008375,"output":0.00696,"cacheRead":0.002464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.017799000000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776693018212}}
