 it**\n- major eras of web3 marketing\n- what worked in bull vs bear markets\n- ecosystem-specific growth patterns\n- narrative timing\n- community/culture effects on distribution\n- repeated mistakes and overused patterns\n\nSo basically: I won’t just “read posts” — I’ll turn them into a **crypto/web3 marketing pattern library** for the agency.\n\nIf you want, next I can give you the **exact structure** I’ll use to summarize each TPan insight so memory stays clean instead of becoming a swamp.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0956d56a4dd30d7c0169e63352cc488191a82e943c42ebbcbc\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":348,"output":276,"cacheRead":19200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19824,"cost":{"input":0.0008700000000000001,"output":0.0041400000000000005,"cacheRead":0.0048,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00981}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776694096682}}
